  "usage_notes": {
    "how_to_use": "Match drug names from DDI pairs against these lists. If both drugs belong to high-risk classes (especially same class or known dangerous combination like MAOI+serotonergic), elevate severity score.",
    "caveats": [
      "Lists are not exhaustive - new drugs may not be included",
      "Some drugs appear in multiple categories (e.g., SSRIs are both QT-prolonging and serotonergic)",
